        <item>
            <title>【CES 2024】Honda 推出 Honda 0 系列概念電動車  「H」品牌標誌將於 2026 年啟用</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/14/honda-launch-honda-0-series/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=honda-launch-honda-0-series</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/14/honda-launch-honda-0-series/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蔣納偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 08:24:50 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES 2024]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Honda]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1214874</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Honda 於 2024 年 CES 展會上首次展示了旗下下一代電動車的概念車型——「Honda 0 系列」，預計於 2026 年在美國市場推出。同時，Honda 還推出了專為下一代電動車設計的全新無邊框「H 標誌」徽章。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1214897" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-32-694x389.png" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-32-694x389.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-32.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1214922" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-44-694x463.png" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-44-694x463.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-44.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1214923" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-45-694x412.png" alt="" width="694" height="412" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-45-694x412.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-45.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Honda 0 系列包括 Saloon 和 Space-Hub 兩款概念車，均採用楔形設計，預覽了該日本品牌專為電動車打造的下一代車型。Saloon 作為 Honda 0 系列的旗艦車型，擁有寬大、低矮且稜角分明的運動跑車外形。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1214917" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-41-694x461.png" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-41-694x461.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-41.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Honda 表示，Honda 0 系列車型的核心概念是「以人為本/機器為輔」，表明了 Honda 對於駕駛優先、性能和輕量化效率的承諾，儘管車輛配備了被車迷視為對駕駛體驗成負面影響的，轉向線控技術和基於機器人技術的自動駕駛技術。Honda 承諾，基於 Honda 0 Saloon 概念車的量產車型將於 2026 年推出時，仍將保留「駕駛的樂趣」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1214924" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-46-694x462.png" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-46-694x462.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-46.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Honda 0 系列電動車概念車將配備 e 軸，將電動馬達與車輪直接對齊，而不是放在引擎艙內，並配備緊湊、高密度的電池組，以最大化內部空間。Honda 承諾，量產車型將實現「無壓力充電」，預計 10 至 15 分鐘內可實現 15% 至 80% 的充電，並「最大程度減少電池性能隨時間退化」，目標是在 10 年駕駛後電池容量損失不超過 10%。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1214920" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-43-694x462.png" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-43-694x462.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-43.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.cnet.com/roadshow/news/honda-debuts-two-0-series-ev-concepts-aimed-at-2026-production/">cnet</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/rog-phone-8-pro-first-review/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】ROG Phone 8 / 8 Pro　外形　手感　設計　規格開箱評測 + 與 ROG Phone 7 比對</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/nvidia-rtx-4070-super-unboxing/parts/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【開箱】NVIDIA RTX 4070 SUPER 顯示卡　搶先看 Founder Edition 真身</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/13/invoxia-minitailz/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】測量貓咪狗仔心跳 + 追蹤位置   invoxia Minitailz 全新寵物智能頸圈</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/14/honda-launch-honda-0-series/life-tech/auto/">【CES 2024】Honda 推出 Honda 0 系列概念電動車  「H」品牌標誌將於 2026 年啟用</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
